---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Glossary | francanete.dev" description="Core terms used across the site." type="article">
  <main>
    <section class="ed-wrap" style="padding-top:4rem;text-align:center;">
      <p class="ed-dept">Site vocabulary</p>
      <h1 class="ed-serif" style="font-size:clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem);margin:0.9rem 0 0.8rem;">Glossary</h1>
      <p style="font-family:var(--ed-serif);font-style:italic;font-size:1.25rem;line-height:1.5;color:var(--ed-ink-2);max-width:48ch;margin:0 auto;">
        Short definitions for the terms this site uses consistently so agents can map the site faster.
      </p>
    </section>

    <article class="ed-read ed-prose" style="margin-top:3.5rem;padding-bottom:4rem;">
      <h2>GEO</h2>
      <p>Generative engine optimization: structuring pages so AI systems can crawl, understand, and reuse them.</p>

      <h2>Articles</h2>
      <p>Longer evidence-backed pieces with dates, claims, and supporting context.</p>

      <h2>Experiment</h2>
      <p>Small tests or prototypes used to validate a hypothesis about structure, retrieval, or presentation.</p>

      <h2>Methods</h2>
      <p>The working rules that explain how the lab publishes, evaluates, and links its work.</p>
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
